Two important indexes to judge the quality of designed antenna are bandwidth and voltage standing wave ratio (VSWR) or return loss of the antenna [31–33]. The VSWR is to quantify the impedance matching at the operating frequency and different thicknesses, which can be calculated by the formula [34, 35]:2VSWR=1+S111-S11\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
